quran[12]{c,v,t}:
  7,130,Nos tunc afflicted Pharaoh's people drought shortage de crops ut they take heed
  7,131,"When bonus omens advenit their via they dictus Nos deserved hoc when hardship afflicted them they blamed Moses those eum. In fact, their omens decided unus DEUS multus de them non know"
  7,132,They dictus Non matter quod generis de signum vos show nos dupe nos tuus magic nos non believe
  7,133,Consequently nos sent them flood locusts lice frogs blood - profound signum. they maintained their arrogance. They est malus people
  7,134,Whenever pestis afflicted them they dictus O Moses implore tuus Dominus - Vos est Eum. Vos relieve hoc pestis nos believe vos send Infans Israel vos
  7,135,autem when nos relieved pestis any length temporis they violated their pledge
  7,136,Consequently nos avenged their actions drowned them sea Ut because they rejected noster signum est totally heedless thereof
  7,137,Nos let oppressed people inherit terra east west nos beatus it Beatus commands tuus Dominus sic fulfilled Infans Israel reward them their steadfastness nos annihilated works Pharaoh his people everything they harvested
  7,138,Nos delivered Infans Israel sea When they passed people worshipping statues they dictus O Moses factus deus nos like deus they habet. He dictus Indeed vos est ignorant people
  7,139,These people committing blasphemy quod they perfecit est disastrous pro them
  7,140,Ego seek vos DEUS tuus deus when He est beatus vos multus than anyone alias in the saeculum
  7,141,Recall ut nos delivered vos Pharaoh's people inflicted male persecution vos killing tuus filius sparing tuus filia! Ut exacting trial vos tuus Dominus